 to where our village lay', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'In-shore among the alder-trees and pollards', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 66, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/c3252244', name: 'The village lay on the flat in-shore', category: 'STATE_CHANGE', location: 'In-shore among the alder-trees and pollards', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 67, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/9f001460', name: 'The village is a mile or more from the church', category: 'STATE_CHANGE', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 68, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/dd91579f', name: 'The man looked at me for a moment', category: 'INTERPERSONAL_INTERACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 69, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e5999113', name: 'The man turned me upside down', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 70, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/0515cfe8', name: 'The man emptied my pockets', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 71, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/b5132118', name: 'There was nothing in my pockets but a piece of bread', category: 'DISCOVERY', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 72, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/7f75ae0e', name: 'The church came to itself', category: 'ADAPTATION_TO_CHANGE', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 73, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/406fff5b', name: 'The man made the church go head over heels before me', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 74, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/45230b6a', name: 'I saw the steeple under my feet', category: 'PERCEPTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', chapter: 1, sequence: 75, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/c00dd5a1', name: 'I was seated on a high tombstone', category: 'STATE_CHANGE', location: 'Near the church', time: 'Afternoon', cha