E', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 87, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/927156bf', name: 'I held tighter to the tombstone', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 88, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/0995bdaf', name: 'I wanted to keep myself upon the tombstone', category: 'ASPIRATION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 89, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/2b1b219c', name: 'I wanted to keep myself from crying', category: 'ASPIRATION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 90, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/29a404b2', name: 'I felt the urge to cry', category: 'EMOTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 91, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/b5354e05', name: 'The man asked where the mother was', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 92, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/0ef10519', name: 'He started', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 93, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/94a02a6c', name: 'He made a short run', category: 'PHYSICAL_MOVEMENT', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 94, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/b3a6d13e', name: 'He stopped', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 95, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/617d5411', name: 'He looked over his shoulder', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 96, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/8da31409', name: 'I timidly explained', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 97, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e6fbda0e', name: 'Georgiana is identified as my mother', category: 'ACKNOWLEDGMENT', location: 'Near the church', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 98, quot