, sequence: 130, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/6fe10185', name: 'The speaker felt fear due to the convict\'s threats.', category: 'CHARACTER_EMOTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 131, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/8b6a33ee', name: 'The narrator felt dreadfully frightened', category: 'CHARACTER_EMOTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 132, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/dc1ac5b4', name: 'The narrator felt giddy', category: 'CHARACTER_EMOTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 133, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e0be1924', name: 'The narrator clung to him with both hands', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 134, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/16bbe0a4', name: 'The narrator asked him to let her keep upright', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 135, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/d992f2e1', name: 'The narrator expressed hope that she wouldn\'t be sick', category: 'EMOTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 136, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/963fa2e5', name: 'The narrator expressed hope that she could attend more', category: 'EMOTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 137, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e6b28a9d', name: 'He gave me a most tremendous dip and roll', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 138, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/53674984', name: 'the church jumped over its own weathercock', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 139, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/403c6072', name: 'He held me by the arms', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Tombstone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 140, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/0e319c6f', name: 'I was in an upright position on the top of the stone', category: 'STATE_CHANGE', location: 'top of the stone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 141, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e904459c', name: 'He went on in these fearful terms', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'top of the stone', time: 'At that time', chapter: 1, sequence: 142, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/06d10836', name: 'The convict demands the file and food to be brought to him', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 143, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/4d37e8fe', name: 'The convict threatens Pip with violence if he fails to comply', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 144, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/fa1c293c', name: 'The convict reveals he is not alone and that there is another young man with him', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 145, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/d4c3193a', name: 'The convict claims the young man with him is better than himself', category: 'DIALOGUE', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 146, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/eb4191fb', name: 'Pip feels fear in response to the convict\'s threats', category: 'EMOTION', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 147, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/397d6b99', name: 'A young man has a secret way of getting at a boy.', category: 'DISCOVERY', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 148, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/c7303445', name: 'A boy attempts to hide himself from the young man.', category: 'GOAL_DRIVEN_ACTION', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 149, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/e6142e95', name: 'A boy locks his door.', category: 'PHYSICAL_ACTION', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow morning', chapter: 1, sequence: 150, quote: ''}, {id: 'event/1150b828', name: 'A boy is warm in bed.', category: 'STATE_CHANGE', location: 'Old Battery', time: 'Tomorrow 